{"id": "14716", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14716", "title": "Rifthome Axe", "text": "Rifthome Axe is an enchanted throwing axe +3 which returns instantly to the wielder after being thrown - Available only in or .\nGameplay.\nThis one-handed axe is a +3 &lt;a href=\"Enchanted%20item\"&gt;Enchanted item&lt;/a&gt;, that can be used as throwing weapon of a traditional melee weapon.\nIt weighs 2 lbs. and has a speed factor of 1. One needs at least 4 &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; to wield this weapon.\nIf thrown, the axe has a 20-feet range and inflicts 1d6+3 &lt;a href=\"Missile%20damage\"&gt;Missile damage&lt;/a&gt;, with a 3-point &lt;a href=\"THAC0\"&gt;THAC0&lt;/a&gt; bonus and which is modified by the user's strength modifier.\nIn melee the axe has a 1-foot range and inflicts 1d6+3 &lt;a href=\"Slashing%20damage\"&gt;Slashing damage&lt;/a&gt;, with a 3-point &lt;a href=\"THAC0\"&gt;THAC0&lt;/a&gt; bonus and which is modified by the user's strength modifier.\nAcquisition.\n&lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; must side with &lt;a href=\"Bodhi\"&gt;Bodhi&lt;/a&gt; and undertake the &lt;a href=\"Perform%20Bodhi%27s%20Tasks%20to%20Receive%20Her%20Aid\"&gt;Perform Bodhi's Tasks to Receive Her Aid&lt;/a&gt; questline in order to have a shot at obtaining this weapon.\nIt can be recovered from the corpse of &lt;a href=\"Arkanis%20Gath\"&gt;Arkanis Gath&lt;/a&gt; after succeeding in the first task set forth by Bodhi during &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20II%20Chapter%203\"&gt;Chapter 3&lt;/a&gt;."}
