{"id": "8329", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8329", "title": "Strong Arm", "text": "Strong Arm is an enchanted composite longbow +2, but it requires a Strength of 19 points to be able to use this weapon, which means that only &lt;a href=\"Dorn%20II-Khan\"&gt;Dorn II-Khan&lt;/a&gt; in the Enhanced Edition can wield it without a strength boosting item. It adds a +3 damage bonus and -3 THAC0 bonus to arrows fired from this weapon.\nThis bow is sold exclusively by &lt;a href=\"Ribald%20Barterman\"&gt;Ribald Barterman&lt;/a&gt;.\nBugs.\nEarlier versions of the game listed the item as having a weight of 7lbs. and a speed factor of 4 in the item description. This is corrected in the enhanced edition."}
