{"id": "49970", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49970", "title": "Sun Soul Horvat", "text": "The Monk Sun Soul Horvat is a character from . He is one of the heretic monks being trained and evaluated by the Beastmaster &lt;a href=\"Jolstead\"&gt;Jolstead&lt;/a&gt;, nearby the animal pens and cages South of the &lt;a href=\"Heretic%20Temple\"&gt;Heretic Temple&lt;/a&gt;. \nGameplay.\nHorvat has all the abilities, immunities and special bonuses afforded to a Sun Soul Monk kit commensurate with his 7th Level experience. If made hostile, he will attack in monk fashion using fists and kicks.\nMod content.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; mod provides a new AI monk script. Three potions are provided to him and scripted for use to heal or boost abilities."}
