{"id": "55322", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=55322", "title": "Tat", "text": "Tat is Jan's niece. Tat and her brother &lt;a href=\"Tot\"&gt;Tot&lt;/a&gt; are seen and heard as part of the &lt;a href=\"Jan%20Jansen%20Summoned%20Home\"&gt;Jan Jansen Summoned Home&lt;/a&gt; questline when first entering the Jansen home.\nGameplay.\nShe and her brother are excited to see Jan return, and the two siblings shout in glee - arguing and playfully scampering about.\nTat is protective of her kitty and doesn't want Tot to use one of Jan's &lt;a href=\"Flasher%20Master%20Bruiser%20Mate\"&gt;Flasher Master Bruiser Mate&lt;/a&gt; at the cat.\nThe party can speak to her if they wish.\nShe and her brother are provided as actors to spice up the storyline. Harming these children counts as attacking an innocent, so expect up a -10 &lt;a href=\"Reputation\"&gt;Reputation&lt;/a&gt; loss if one of them is killed."}
