{"id": "27374", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=27374", "title": "Tavern Bouncer", "text": "During the &lt;a href=\"party\"&gt;party&lt;/a&gt;'s arrival in \"&lt;a href=\"the%20Black%20Pits\"&gt;the Black Pits&lt;/a&gt;\", a tavern bouncer \u2013 a male &lt;a href=\"dwarven\"&gt;dwarven&lt;/a&gt; fighter \u2013 can be witnessed being confused about this place he and some other &lt;a href=\"tavern\"&gt;tavern&lt;/a&gt;ers surprisingly just have been &lt;a href=\"Dimension%20Door\"&gt;teleported&lt;/a&gt; to.\nBackground.\nNothing is known about his origin, personal life, or at which tavern he has been a bouncer. Also his name is never revealed. The tavern bouncer remains an unknown victim of the Pits.\nInvolvement.\nBeing the quickest of the three to realize the situation, he notices that they are in some fighting pit when suddenly appear. As the others, he will be attacked by one of the three &lt;a href=\"Tasloi%20%28The%20Black%20Pits%29\"&gt;tasloi&lt;/a&gt;, draws a &lt;a href=\"short%20sword\"&gt;short sword&lt;/a&gt; and defends himself, but has no chance to survive against the &lt;a href=\"spear\"&gt;spear&lt;/a&gt; wielder. Soon he will lie in the arena sand, not far from the gate but never able to leave through it."}
