{"id": "4260", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4260", "title": "Telescope", "text": "The Telescope is a quest item needed for a side quest in the city of &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28city%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt;. In the &lt;a href=\"Elfsong%20Tavern\"&gt;Elfsong Tavern&lt;/a&gt;, a gnome named &lt;a href=\"Brevlik\"&gt;Brevlik&lt;/a&gt; requests that &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; and party steal this item from the &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Wonders\"&gt;Hall of Wonders&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "7561", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7561", "title": "Telka", "text": "Telka, along with &lt;a href=\"Maneira\"&gt;Maneira&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Zeela\"&gt;Zeela&lt;/a&gt;, is a member of &lt;a href=\"Lamalha\"&gt;Lamalha&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"Little%20amazons\"&gt;assassin group&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Valley%20of%20the%20Tombs\"&gt;Valley of the Tombs&lt;/a&gt; area located east of the &lt;a href=\"Nashkel\"&gt;Nashkel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"carnival\"&gt;carnival&lt;/a&gt;. They have been sent by the &lt;a href=\"Iron%20Throne\"&gt;Iron Throne&lt;/a&gt; to kill &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt;.\nTelka prefers to attack at range with her &lt;a href=\"Longbow\"&gt;Longbow&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Arrow%20of%20Fire\"&gt;Arrows of Fire&lt;/a&gt;, but also has a &lt;a href=\"Short%20Sword\"&gt;Short Sword&lt;/a&gt; if engaged in melee. She wears &lt;a href=\"Studded%20Leather%20Armor%20%2B1\"&gt;Studded Leather Armor +1&lt;/a&gt;."}
