f%20the%20Princes%20%2B1\"&gt;Ring of the Princes +1&lt;/a&gt; \u2013 that &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; can request the three new apprentices; &lt;a href=\"Morul\"&gt;Morul&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Larz\"&gt;Larz&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Nara\"&gt;Nara&lt;/a&gt;, to attempt to complete to begin their magical training."}
