{"id": "37007", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=37007", "title": "Dead Man's Pass", "text": "Dead Man's Pass is an area in chapter 10 of . This pass lies directly between the &lt;a href=\"Coalition%20Camp\"&gt;Coalition Camp&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dragonspear%20Castle\"&gt;Dragonspear Castle&lt;/a&gt;, and as such must be explored before the latter location can be reached.\nThe area provides elements required for the solution of several quests, including &lt;a href=\"Anniversary%20Gift\"&gt;Anniversary Gift&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0and &lt;a href=\"Helvdar%27s%20Lucky%20Charm\"&gt;Helvdar's Lucky Charm&lt;/a&gt;.\nConnections.\nThe area is reached by travelling north from the &lt;a href=\"Coalition%20Camp\"&gt;Coalition Camp&lt;/a&gt;, and allows onward travel to &lt;a href=\"Dragonspear%C2%A0Castle\"&gt;Dragonspear\u00a0Castle&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0to the north-west, and both &lt;a href=\"Bloodbark%20Grove\"&gt;Bloodbark Grove&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0and &lt;a href=\"Underground%20River\"&gt;Underground River&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0to the east.\nIt is necessary to pass-through Dead Man's Pass to reach Dragonspear Castle, whilst Underground River requires transit through either here, or Bloodbark Grove (which can be reached directly from the Coalition Camp)."}
